products.title: Galaxy Anthracite Grey Roman Blind
products.description: Simple styling with a unique twist, the galaxy anthracite roman blind will enhance a modern living space, bedroom or study. This smart blind will give your space a sleek update with an easy to operate design and cool contemporary colour palette. The grey, woven fabric benefits from a twinkling added touch created by metallic yarns. Product id: db-rom1021 fabric colour: anthracite grey material: 60% polyester 40% viscose lining: light filtering poly/cotton blended lining headrail: durable white headrail with top or face fix brackets.
